==========================================================================
   haddoc: A Tool to Browse HTML Python Documentation From Command-Line
==========================================================================



- A simple Python script that will parse the various HTML indexes of the Python
  documentation and create some kind of searcheable database.

- A simple command-line tool that will search that database and bring a web
  browser to that documentation.

- An emacs hook that can call this tool to bring up a browser with the
  given documentation.


